# ─── PBR texture variants we don't use (DirectX normals, raw roughness, preview thumbs) ───
# Keep NormalGL + Color + Displacement + AO + Metalness; reject the rest
Assets/_Project/Textures/PBR/**/*_NormalDX.png
Assets/_Project/Textures/PBR/**/*_Roughness.png
Assets/_Project/Textures/PBR/**/*_NormalDX.png.meta
Assets/_Project/Textures/PBR/**/*_Roughness.png.meta
# AmbientCG preview thumbnails (root of each set)
Assets/_Project/Textures/PBR/*/[A-Z]*[0-9].png
Assets/_Project/Textures/PBR/*/[A-Z]*[0-9].png.meta

